{"name": "djangocms-meta-og", "metadata": {"name": "djangocms-meta-og", "version": "1.0.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 5 - Production/Stable", "Environment :: Web Environment", "Framework :: Django CMS", "Framework :: Django CMS :: 3.4", "Framework :: Django CMS :: 4.1", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: BSD License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Topic :: Internet :: WWW/HTTP", "Topic :: Internet :: WWW/HTTP :: Dynamic Content", "Topic :: Software Development", "Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries", "Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Application Frameworks"], "home_page": null, "license": "MIT License", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["django-cms", "django-meta-og"], "summary": "DjangoCMS HTML Meta tags for OpenGraph.", "upload_time": 1734086299}, "documentation": ["# DjangoCMS Meta OG\n\n\nHTML Meta tags [OpenGraph](https://ogp.me/) for [DjangoCMS](https://www.django-cms.org/).\nThe project is based on the [Django Meta OG](https://gitlab.nic.cz/django-apps/django-meta-og) project.\n\n### Install\n\n`pip install djangocms-meta-og`\n\n\nAdd into settings.py:\n\n```python\nINSTALLED_APPS = [\n    \"django_meta_og\",\n    \"djangocms_meta_og\",\n    ...\n]\n\nTEMPLATES  = [\n    {\"OPTIONS\": {\n            \"context_processors\": [\n                \"djangocms_meta_og.context_processors.meta\",\n                ...\n            ]\n        }\n    }\n]\n```\n\nAdd into the templates:\n\n```django\n{% load djangocms_meta_og %}\n{% djangocms_meta_og_prefix as og_prefix %}\n<head{% if og_prefix %} prefix=\"{{ og_prefix }}\"{% endif %}>\n    {% include \"django_meta_og/header_meta.html\" %}\n```\n\nThe result can be:\n\n```html\n<head prefix=\"og: https://ogp.me/ns#\">\n    <meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\" />\n    <meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"The Title\" />\n    ...\n</head>\n```\n\n### License\n\nBSD License\n"], "modules": [{"name": "djangocms_meta_og.utils", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "djangocms_meta_og.utils.get_page_meta", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "current_page", "type": {"name": "Page", "xref": {"fqname": "cms.models.Page", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "language", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "PageMetaOg", "xref": {"fqname": "djangocms_meta_og.utils.models.PageMetaOg", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["Get meta OG for current page."]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "djangocms_meta_og.migrations.0001_initial", "documentation": ["Generated by Django 4.2.6 on 2024-12-12 09:27"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "djangocms_meta_og.migrations.0001_initial.Migration", "bases": ["migrations.Migration"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "djangocms_meta_og.migrations.0001_initial.Migration.initial", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "djangocms_meta_og.migrations.0001_initial.Migration.dependencies", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "djangocms_meta_og.migrations.0001_initial.Migration.operations", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "djangocms_meta_og.migrations", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "djangocms_meta_og.templatetags", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "djangocms_meta_og.tests", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "djang